<h2>Why People Are Buying Ember Mug² 14oz</h2>
<p>Coffee gets cold. It's a universal frustration — you brew a perfect cup, get distracted, and come back to lukewarm disappointment. Microwaving ruins the flavor. The Ember Mug became popular because it promises to keep your coffee at the perfect temperature indefinitely.</p>

<h2>What Is Ember Mug² 14oz?</h2>
<p>The Ember Mug² is a battery-powered smart mug with a built-in heating element. You set your preferred temperature (120°F–145°F) via the Ember app, and the mug maintains it. It sits on a charging coaster that keeps it powered and warm indefinitely. It went viral when tech reviewers called it 'the iPhone of coffee mugs.'</p>
<p><strong>Why it went viral:</strong> Tech reviewers calling it the most luxurious way to drink coffee</p>

<h2>How to Use Ember Mug² 14oz</h2>
<ol>
    <li><strong>1.</strong> Download the Ember app and pair your mug via Bluetooth</li>
    <li><strong>2.</strong> Set your preferred drinking temperature between 120°F and 145°F</li>
    <li><strong>3.</strong> Pour your coffee and the mug will heat it to your set temperature within minutes</li>
    <li><strong>4.</strong> Place on the included charging coaster when not carrying to maintain temperature and charge</li>
</ol>

